longBusinessSummary: Rand Mining Limited explores for, develops, and produces mineral properties in Australia. It explores for gold and silver deposits. The company holds a 12.25% interest in the East Kundana Joint Venture located to the west north west of Kalgoorlie and north east of Coolgardie. It also has a 50% interest in the Seven Mile Hill project. The company was incorporated in 1966 and is based in South Perth, Australia.
